---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import PageTitle from '../components/PageTitle.astro';

const title = 'Richard Waine Photography Studio - Lancaster PA';
const h1 = 'Richard Waine Photography Studio';
---

<MainLayout title="Richard Waine Headshot Photography | Location" description="Richard Waine Photography is centrally located in downtown Lancaster, PA. Specializing in professional headshots, portraiture, and personal branding.">

<main>
  <div class="studio-page">

      <PageTitle title={h1} titleColor="var(--ltclr)" />

      <div class="wrapper layout">


      <!-- Header Section -->
          <section id="header">
            <div class="">

              <p>
                Richard Waine Photography is located in the heart of downtown Lancaster, Pennsylvania, directly across the street from Fulton Bank, and diagonal from the Lancaster County Convention Center.
              </p>
              
              <p>
                The studio sits directly next to Lancaster Central Market and is a stone's throw from the major highways as well as the Lancaster Train Station.
              </p>

            </div>
          </section>

      <!-- Content and Map Section -->
          <section id="content-map">
            
              <div class="grid">
                    <div class="content">
                      <p>One of Lancaster's famed attractions is the Lancaster Central Market, the country's oldest farmers market. You can find regional food specialties, preserves, and a wide variety of flavors.</p>

                      <p>Downtown Lancaster is full of interesting restaurants and shops. A visit to Lancaster isn't complete without taking in a show at the Fulton Theatre. The productions are always fantastic and incredibly well done.</p>

                      <p>If you schedule your session during baseball season, take a trip to Clipper Stadium to see the Lancaster Barnstormers play some top notch ball!</p>

                      <p>When you stop by to update your headshot images, make sure to allow some time to explore the city.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="map">
                      <iframe
                        src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3054.651336472875!2d-76.305992!3d40.0385633!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x89c627a7edfcfd67%3A0x9f55d6775e366e9a!2sRichard%20Waine%20Photography!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1760976227043!5m2!1sen!2sus"
                        width="100%"
                        height="400"
                        style="border:0;"
                        allowfullscreen=""
                        loading="lazy"
                        referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
                      </iframe>
                    </div>
              </div>
           
          </section>
   
   
   
    </div>
</div>
</main>

</MainLayout>

<style>

 
  .studio-page {
   
    background: var(--drkbg);
    min-height:100vh;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;
  
  }

.layout{
  height:calc(100% - var(--header-height));
  display: grid;
  align-content: center;
  gap: var(--size-7);
  margin-block:var(--size-7); 
}



  #header p {
    font-size: var(--fs-450);
    color: var(--ltclr);
    margin-bottom: var(--size-7);
    line-height:var(--line-height-relaxed);
   
  }

  #header p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  #content-map {
    margin-top: var(--size-7);
    background: var(--drkbg);
  }

 .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--size-7);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .content p {
    font-size: var(--fs-450);
    color: var(--ltclr);
    line-height:var(--line-height-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--size-7);
  }

  .content p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .map iframe {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius:var(--size-2);
    box-shadow:var(--shadow);
  }



  /* ==========================================
   DESKTOP - min-width: 64em (1024px)
   ========================================== */
  @media (min-width: 64em) {
  .grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  }
  }
/* ==========================================
   LARGE DESKTOP - min-width: 90em (1440px)
   ========================================== */

 @media (min-width: 90em) {
   .layout{
  margin-block:0; /*added for mobile */

   }}


</style>

</MainLayout>
